{
  "stem": "15197.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was afraid to jump, not knowing too much about dynamite, that maybe this could explode.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was on top and the shooting came closer and I was sure that I am done.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But suddenly, the two people who were waiting for me saw me there on top and they made a human ladder from the ghetto side and brought me down.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we ran away just in time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was another time of smuggling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A third time I remember also while I smuggled in dynamite it was in a factory, [INAUDIBLE] factory, on [POLISH] Street, which one part of the factory was on the Polish side where the door was.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other side, where the windows were, were on the Jewish, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told me that this is going to be the best way how to smuggle in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, I came in and the guide, which is guarding, was there and he let me in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was having this vis-a-vis opposite the factory is the Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was a German guarding [INAUDIBLE] cemetery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I got in into the factory and he told me-- he took me to the window there and told me, OK, give me your package.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't know what I'm smuggling in, the Polish guard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the package didn't go through the window.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have to repack this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I start repack it together with him and he was terribly nervous.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was nervous, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the people on the other side from the ghetto were calling, faster, faster, faster.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally, I made it in smaller packages and we pushed it through.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
